1
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:05,370
如果彼得在耶路撒冷
If Peter is in Jerusalem,

2
00:00:05,380 --> 00:00:07,170
我会找到他的
I will find him.

3
00:00:07,270 --> 00:00:08,090
他知道我是谁
He knows who I am.

4
00:00:08,190 --> 00:00:11,000
我已经不是那个你们理应憎恨的人了
I'm not the same man you once had reason to hate.

5
00:00:11,050 --> 00:00:11,990
你看见了谁?
Who did you see?

6
00:00:12,190 --> 00:00:16,440
我看见耶稣基督 神的儿子
I saw Jesus Christ, the son of God.

7
00:00:16,510 --> 00:00:18,300
教我如何杀人
Show me how to kill.

8
00:00:19,140 --> 00:00:21,630
收回那些话 卡里古拉
Take back those words, Caligula

9
00:00:21,630 --> 00:00:24,400
不然我就割了你的喉咙
before I open your throat.

10
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:25,440
来啊
Do it.

11
00:00:25,440 --> 00:00:29,250
你在期待罗马的新职位吗?
Were you looking forward to your new position in Rome?

12
00:00:29,250 --> 00:00:34,050
跪下!! 跪拜你的新大帝!
Kneel!! In the presence of your new emperor!!

13
00:00:34,050 --> 00:00:36,560
扫罗已经成了耶稣的信徒了
Saul has become a follower of Jesus.

14
00:00:36,570 --> 00:00:39,310
你不能在犹太会堂传耶稣的道
You can't preach the word of jesus inside the Synagogue.

15
00:00:39,310 --> 00:00:41,310
我们恰恰必须这样做
That is exactly what we have to do.

16
00:00:44,110 --> 00:00:46,050
他会把我们都害死的!
He's gonna get us all killed!

17
